<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <%- include('head') %>
  <title><%= locals.title %></title>
  <meta name="description" content="<%= locals.description %>" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="<%= locals.title %>" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="<%= locals.description %>" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://oldschoolgames.eu/about" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="OldSchoolGames" />
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://oldschoolgames.eu/images/navbar.webp" />
  <script type="application/ld+json">
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "OldSchoolGames.eu",
        "url": "https://oldschoolgames.eu",
        "logo": "https://oldschoolgames.eu/favicon.png",
        "description": "A hobby project dedicated to preserving and celebrating classic MS-DOS games from the 80s and 90s.",
        "founder": {
          "@type": "Person",
          "name": "RobLib",
          "url": "https://roblib.dev",
          "sameAs": [
            "https://github.com/RobertLib",
            "https://twitter.com/RobertLibsansky"
          ]
        },
        "contactPoint": {
          "@type": "ContactPoint",
          "contactType": "Customer Support",
          "email": "contact@oldschoolgames.eu"
        }
      }
    </script>
</head>

<body class="layout">
  <%- include('navbar') %> <%- include('left-sidebar') %>
  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <%- include('flash') %>
      <section>
        <h1 class="text-lg" style="margin-bottom: 20px">
          About OldSchoolGames.eu
        </h1>

        <h2 class="text-md" style="margin-bottom: 10px">
          What is this site?
        </h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 15px">
          OldSchoolGames.eu is a hobby project dedicated to preserving and
          celebrating classic
          <strong>MS-DOS games from the 1980s and 1990s</strong>. The goal is
          to make it easy for anyone to rediscover the games that shaped the
          history of PC gaming — playable directly in your browser, no
          installation required.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 25px">
          Games run through <strong>js-dos</strong>, a JavaScript port of the
          legendary
          <a class="color-primary underline" href="https://www.dosbox.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DOSBox</a>
          emulator. Everything works inside a standard web browser — nothing
          to install, just click and play.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-md" style="margin-bottom: 10px">Who runs this?</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 15px">
          This site is created and maintained by
          <strong>RobLib</strong>, a software developer and retro
          gaming enthusiast based in the Czech Republic.
        </p>
        <ul style="margin-bottom: 25px; padding-left: 20px; line-height: 2">
          <li>
            Personal site:
            <a class="color-primary underline" href="https://roblib.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">roblib.dev</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            GitHub:
            <a class="color-primary underline" href="https://github.com/RobertLib" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/RobertLib</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            X (Twitter):
            <a class="color-primary underline" href="https://twitter.com/RobertLibsansky" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@RobertLibsansky</a>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-md" style="margin-bottom: 10px">Open Source</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 25px">
          The source code for this project is publicly available on GitHub:
          <a class="color-primary underline" href="https://github.com/RobertLib/old-school-games" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/RobertLib/old-school-games</a>. Contributions, bug reports, and feedback are always welcome.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-md" style="margin-bottom: 10px">Copyright & Games</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 15px">
          This site hosts games that are believed to be freely distributable —
          including titles officially released as freeware by their
          publishers, and classic abandonware titles no longer commercially
          available. We do not profit from the games hosted on this platform.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 25px">
          If you are a copyright holder and believe any content hosted here
          infringes your rights, please contact us via our
          <a class="color-primary underline" href="/dmca">DMCA policy page</a>
          and we will remove it promptly.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-md" style="margin-bottom: 10px">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For general inquiries, game suggestions, or copyright concerns,
          reach out at
          <a class="color-primary underline" href="mailto:contact@oldschoolgames.eu">contact@oldschoolgames.eu</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  <%- include('right-sidebar') %> <%- include('footer') %>
</body>

</html>
